│ My analysis of the bug indicates that the crash occurs during loop-invariant code motion   │
│ (LICM) when trying to promote a store out of a loop. The promotion logic incorrectly       │
│ attempts to sink a store into a block that is part of an outer loop, violating MemorySSA's │
│ dominance requirements.                                                                    │
│                                                                                            │
│ Specifically, `LoopPromoter::insertStoresInLoopExitBlocks` is responsible for creating new │
│ stores in the exit blocks of the loop from which an access is being promoted. In the       │
│ provided reproducer, `loop1` has one exit block, `loop1.exit`. This exit block has         │
│ multiple successors, one of which (`loop0.latch`) is part of the outer loop `loop0`. The   │
│ logic for placing the new store does not account for this, and it tries to place a store   │
│ in `loop0.latch`. However, `loop0.latch` is dominated by `loop1`'s header. When            │
│ `MemorySSAUpdater` tries to insert this new store, it finds that the new `MemoryDef` in    │
│ `loop0.latch` does not dominate the original memory access location inside `loop1`,        │
│ leading to an assertion failure.                                                           │
│                                                                                            │
│ The fix is to prevent `LoopPromoter` from inserting stores into blocks that are dominated  │
│ by the loop header from which the promotion is occurring. This requires passing the `Loop` │
│ and `DominatorTree` pointers to the `LoopPromoter` class and adding a dominance check in   │
│ `insertStoresInLoopExitBlocks` before creating a new store.                                │
│                                                                                            │
│ Here is the patch that implements this fix:                                                │
│                                                                                            │
│ ```patch                                                                                   │
│ --- a/llvm/lib/Transforms/Scalar/LICM.cpp                                                  │
│ +++ b/llvm/lib/Transforms/Scalar/LICM.cpp                                                  │
│ @@ -1767,9 +1767,11 @@                                                                     │
│    SmallVectorImpl<MemoryAccess *> &MSSAInsertPts;                                         │
│    PredIteratorCache &PredCache;                                                           │
│    MemorySSAUpdater &MSSAU;                                                                │
│ +  Loop *L;                                                                                │
│    LoopInfo &LI;                                                                           │
│ +  DominatorTree *DT;                                                                      │
│    DebugLoc DL;                                                                            │
│    Align Alignment;                                                                        │
│    bool UnorderedAtomic;                                                                   │
│ @@ -1795,14 +1797,15 @@                                                                    │
│    LoopPromoter(Value *SP, ArrayRef<const Instruction *> Insts, SSAUpdater &S,             │
│                 SmallVectorImpl<BasicBlock *> &LEB,                                        │
│                 SmallVectorImpl<BasicBlock::iterator> &LIP,                                │
│ -               SmallVectorImpl<MemoryAccess *> &MSSAIP, PredIteratorCache &PIC,           │
│ -               MemorySSAUpdater &MSSAU, LoopInfo &li, DebugLoc dl,                        │
│ -               Align Alignment, bool UnorderedAtomic, const AAMDNodes &AATags,            │
│ -               ICFLoopSafetyInfo &SafetyInfo, bool CanInsertStoresInExitBlocks)           │
│ +               SmallVectorImpl<MemoryAccess *> &MSSAIP, PredIteratorCache &PIC,           │
│ MemorySSAUpdater &MSSAU,                                                                   │
│ +               Loop *L, LoopInfo *LI, DominatorTree *DT, DebugLoc dl, Align Alignment,    │
│ +               bool UnorderedAtomic, const AAMDNodes &AATags,                             │
│ +               ICFLoopSafetyInfo &SafetyInfo,                                             │
│ +               bool CanInsertStoresInExitBlocks)                                          │
│        : LoadAndStorePromoter(Insts, S), SomePtr(SP), LoopExitBlocks(LEB),                 │
│          LoopInsertPts(LIP), MSSAInsertPts(MSSAIP), PredCache(PIC), MSSAU(MSSAU),          │
│ -        LI(li), DL(std::move(dl)), Alignment(Alignment),                                  │
│ -        UnorderedAtomic(UnorderedAtomic), AATags(AATags),                                 │
